Description: This quintessential post-modern home will make you feel at ease even in 2017! With its open floor plan and retro wood moldings in each of the three bedrooms it has a charm that will never go out of style. One special feature that stands out the most in this home is a pink and black bathroom a hallmark trend of the 1950 s that was started by First Lady Mamie Eisenhower s love of pink. A must see.

Description:
(301) 703-8608 - Highland, MD - This quintessential post-modern home will make you feel at ease even in 2017! With its open floor plan and retro wood moldings in each of the three bedrooms, it has a charm that will never go out of style. One special feature that stands out the most in this home is a pink and black bathroom, a hallmark trend of the 1950~s that was started by First Lady Mamie Eisenhower~s love of pink. A must see.
(RLNE3524869) Pet policies - Small Dogs Allowed, Large Dogs Allowed.
